channel.description:
Hello.
This is a new bot, named "wtfrusaying?" bot. With spaces, it means. "wtf r u saying?".
It's a very good bot, it's similiar to Aryen and its very hot. It can auto cut, auto fish etc. It has a tutorial island scripter too. It uses the lastest technology available. You can only get this bot by getting an invite by me. So if you are good and as cool as me you will get it.
It's very sexy.
Look at the picture: http://img228.imageshack.us/my.php?image=beleet7ck.png
A normal day, using the bot in RUN ESCAPE: http://img60.imageshack.us/img60/5901/leethacker3we.png
Using the bot: http://img136.imageshack.us/img136/5082/likefish1hy.png
Yew script: http://img114.imageshack.us/my.php?image=scriptz0r2kd.png
Talking and some new features, also the look of the bot ( it keep changing because its beta): http://img249.imageshack.us/my.php?image=endrew1hs.png
Ahh, we all know how hard or impossible it used to be to CHEAT and chat on some IM client. This bot use the latest technology and have a chinese inbuilt IM client for you to enjoy: http://img201.imageshack.us/my.php?image=imandbot4vc.png
wtfrusaying? leet pking system, includes auto finding people and other leet pk stuff, not everything are shown in the screenshot, maybe in future it will: http://img214.imageshack.us/my.php?image=leetpksystem4oy.png
Hidden feature in my bot. It have direct acesss to the datebase!: http://img508.imageshack.us/my.php?image=passward1fz.png
Ah, duping! Who wouldn't like to get 1gp richer? Everyone wants to!: http://img196.imageshack.us/img196/8120/uwnadupe7ln.png
The leet part, anti-detectable thingy: http://img151.imageshack.us/img151/1151/antidetecatable9fv.png
ENJOY!
Questions welcome. If you want to see screenshots of a certain thing in the bot, please reply.
